scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents note
scopecontent.p: Includes a note that accompanied the original folder. There is some light editing and notes that look as though they were written by Arnow. The last line of page 3 has a cut off appearance and is not entirely readable; page 3 appears to have been a carbon copy, as do pages 1 and 2.
